{"tid":196430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國會否用核武攻打朝鮮？〈蕭若元：最新蕭析〉2017-04-11","createTime":"2017-04-11T09:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T15:56:26.000Z","uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66bbb76b47577b500f7ed5909625792f18fef05c","tid":196430,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:57:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8c_HVXt0yH4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8c_HVXt0yH4&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ce91b5a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8c_HVXt0yH4</a><br />\n<br />\n如果報導正確，只有兩艘航母戰鬥群，其實不夠，因此美國不敢對朝鮮動武，現在所作的一切都是虛張聲勢。<br />\n<br />\n我看，只用兩艘航母，除非侵侵真正的瘋了才會打朝鮮的，其一，美國在中東打了普帝的小弟巴沙爾，侵侵已得罪了高登仔既普帝，如果再在亞洲打人造人19號，面對普帝同人造人19號聯手，只有兩艘航母幫助既韓國一定在火海之中。<br />\n<br />\n其實人造人19號也會選擇戰鬥到底，玩特戰，日本韓國卻希望美國做一個像似樣的老大，唔好生事喇。<br />\n<br />\n侵侵打得金仔，都唔當中國軍力一回事。我要是特朗普，我會神奇轉身準備動用了二艘航母去南海，助香港人7.1爭取自由。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/raindog/1326298014-1556736726.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fraindog%2F1326298014-1556736726.jpg&h=302cabcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/174357_26bcb542e4d2e9bba0f921f1f8b4f6d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F174357_26bcb542e4d2e9bba0f921f1f8b4f6d6.jpg&h=60ca99c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edc5160bbcd3fd5f5e6609ba304d42c7afb2996a","tid":196430,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:59:25.000Z","msg":"大鑊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3861be20e9594b76e650869064391889163c920b","tid":196430,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"【金仔靠嚇】轟美國卡爾文森號戰鬥群駛近 北韓：準備好開戰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170411/large/1491877415_aed1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170411%2Flarge%2F1491877415_aed1.jpg&h=625b6763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝鮮半島局勢升溫，美軍日前發射導彈打擊敍利亞政府軍、被指同時含有警告北韓的意味後，旋即調動「卡爾文森號」航空母艦戰鬥群駛往朝鮮半島水域。北韓強烈反彈，周二警告一旦局勢進一步升級已準備好開戰。<br />\n<br />\n北韓朝中社報道，北韓外交部讉責美軍派航母駛近朝鮮半島海域，又指美國要為這個行為負上全責，「這證明美國入侵北韓的魯莽行為已達至嚴重階段」。<br />\n朝鮮局勢近日漸趨緊張，美國和南韓指北韓進行彈道導彈試驗，北韓就視兩國的年度演習具侵略性。美國第三艦隊下屬的「卡爾文森號」航母戰鬥群日前離開新加坡，改變原定駛往澳洲的任務計劃，轉而前往朝鮮半島附近水域展開行動。美國有線電視新聞網報道，行動是為了對近期北韓的挑釁行為作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170411/56549074\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170411%2F56549074&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=64aa8809\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170411%2F56549074&h=8ba32f1c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170411/56549074</a>"},{"pid":"8568f5a3c896922acc32d53fc26df2bf4eaf27e5","tid":196430,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:00:35.000Z","msg":"A US aircraft carrier-led strike group is headed toward the Western Pacific Ocean near the Korean Peninsula, a US defense official confirmed to CNN.<br />\n<br />\n大意：美軍航空母艦群向西太平洋，倚朝鮮半島海峽進發，美軍官方已向CNN確認。<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<a href=\"http://edition.cnn.com/2017/04/09/politics/navy-korean-peninsula/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2017%2F04%2F09%2Fpolitics%2Fnavy-korean-peninsula%2F&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=31645602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2017%2F04%2F09%2Fpolitics%2Fnavy-korean-peninsula%2F&h=1c39bde5\" target=\"_blank\">http://edition.cnn.com/2017/04/09/politics/navy-korean-peninsula/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6c230c9d01355f7c18d4a538e47c9f89cf7f15","tid":196430,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"燒山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7741e48b2bbe2e3cf98a0e153ed8aba10d9633e5","tid":196430,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stC9H44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstC9H44.jpg&h=5210afc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8aadca201f9635e504c131a93edf2e384128fb07","tid":196430,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/165248_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F165248_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=40f23d1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a306507db7ccd3b0d28b104eb32104540244ff3c","tid":196430,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"金仔快啲炸平首爾"},{"pid":"4ae07749bc7a7ffa3ccfa6cf35fff4677de31358","tid":196430,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba4c934536ceef2ad8ba6fa785f2b619ceef818","tid":196430,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931a3debac87af713c274c77c75b68e690251956","tid":196430,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply